{
  "texts": [
    "Yet, it illustrates that methods beyond conventional architectural or data improvements can radically improve language model capabilities.",
    "Beyond FLOP Efficiency: The Multidimensional Nature of ProgressOur focus on training FLOP efficiency necessarily omits many critical innovations.",
    "Numerous improvements we tested (RMSNorm, learning rate schedules, etc.)",
    "showed minimal FLOP efficiency gains but substantially improved training stability, convergence reliability, or extrapolation capabilities.",
    "Other innovations like Flash Attention reduce wall-clock time and energy consumption without affecting total FLOP operations."
  ]
}